<h1><%= @book.title %></h1>

<h2 class="highest-rating">Highest Rating: <%= @book.highest_rating %></h2>

<h2 class="lowest-rating">Lowest Rating: <%= @book.lowest_rating %></h2>

Reviews:
<% @reviews.each do |review| %>
  <%= review.body %>
  <%= review.user.name %>
  <%= review.rating %>
<% end %>

Average Rating: <%= @book.average_rating %>
